     <div class="banner with-image home-hero" data-banner-image="true" style="background:linear-gradient(0deg ,rgba(38, 37, 38, .2),rgba(38, 37, 38, .2)), url(https://www.ucar.edu/sites/default/files/front/2018-10/El%20Nino%20banner%20front%202.jpg) no-repeat center center; background-size: cover">
      <div class="grid-x align-center-middle">
       <div class="cell text-center">
        <div class="grid-y banner-content">
         <h1 class="cell">
          University Corporation for Atmospheric Research
         </h1>
         <h2 class="cell">
          Serving the Earth system science community
         </h2>
         <div class="cell inner">
          <p>
           UCAR's MetEd is an invaluable online training resource that offers hundreds of hours of educational material for the geosciences, including learning modules on El Niño in both English and Spanish. Join the site's half million registered users and start deepening your knowledge today.
           <a href="https://www.meted.ucar.edu/search/search_results.php?hq=site%3Ameted.ucar.edu&amp;cx=012446052473863902991%3Ar8nkgnwzzsc&amp;cof=FORID%3A11&amp;q=enso">
            Browse our modules
           </a>
          </p>
         </div>
         <div class="cell more">
          <div class="grid-x align-stretch align-center">
           <div class="cell small-6 medium-3 text-right description">
            <span>
             Deepen your El Niño knowledge
            </span>
           </div>
