       <div class="cell mlarge-8 featured-story">
        <div class="grid-x panel related-page-section" data-equalizer="">
         <div class="cell mlarge-6 large-7 figure" data-equalizer-watch="">
          <a href="https://news.ucar.edu/132641/everette-joseph-named-ncar-director">
           <img alt="Everette Joseph" height="400" src="/sites/default/files/big-picture-box/2018-12/Joseph%20Everette%20BPB.jpg" typeof="foaf:Image" width="775"/>
          </a>
         </div>
         <div class="cell mlarge-6 large-5 details" data-equalizer-watch="">
          <h3>
           Everette Joseph named next NCAR director
          </h3>
          <div class="excerpt">
           <p>
            Everette Joseph has been named director of the National Center for Atmospheric Research, following a rigorous international search. He joins NCAR from the University at Albany, State University of New York, where he is director of the Atmospheric Sciences Research Center.
           </p>
          </div>
          <a class="cta-link small white-on-color" href="https://news.ucar.edu/132641/everette-joseph-named-ncar-director">
           Read article
          </a>
         </div>
        </div>
